FBIS3-54760 "drsov001_b_94033" FBIS-SOV-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military Issues Signs Edict on Awards for Border Guards LD3112131793 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1200 GMT 31 Dec 93 LD3112131793 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] In the run up to the new year, Russian President Boris Yeltsin has signed an edict on state awards for border guards. There were 31 privates and officers awarded personal bravery decorations for the bravery they showed while carrying out their military duty to guard the state borders, and 67 people were awarded medals for courage.
